item.title: About me
item.description: Hi there, I’m Rich. Things about me: I love science and the wonders of life I find plants amazingly interesting I love coding and analysing data I have a PhD in molecular biology If you’ve eneded up at this site I’m not sure why, but I hope you gain something from my mad stumblings into learning new techniques around data science!
